00:29:17,740 --> 00:29:19,920
 God can do that.

531
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:26,400
 God can work beyond those means that you can think of.

532
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:32,320
 God can even work contrary to all those means,

533
00:29:32,320 --> 00:29:35,340
 to all those instruments that you can think of.

534
00:29:35,340 --> 00:29:39,320
 In fact, if you think about it, that is the gospel.

535
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:42,520
 That is the good news we found in the Bible.

536
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:47,720
 The providence of God transcends human suffering,

537
